Review the list noting which Reports potentially meet your requirements. Use the Preview tool in the Report window to view the presentation of each Report and further narrow your selection.

Use this as a reference in setting up the Report options that fit your needs. Each heading will be in bold text, and followed by Report options for that heading. Look through the entire list before beginning, as some Reports for some items are in different places.
